<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[Does Rowan end up going to jail for life because she does not want to reveal that Ellie killed Maddie?! Did Rowan never actually send her letters to Mr Wrexham? Did she die in prison?! <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
