              <span id="reviewTextContainer2995980505" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15814877487842951991">I had low expectations for this because I had heard such mixed things about Ruth Ware, but this was SO GOOD. It took so many of the classic thriller components but made them feel fresh and new and I&apos;m a big fan. I cannot wait to see what Ruth comes up with next.</span>
  <span id="freeText15814877487842951991" style="display:none">I had low expectations for this because I had heard such mixed things about Ruth Ware, but this was SO GOOD. It took so many of the classic thriller components but made them feel fresh and new and I'm a big fan. I cannot wait to see what Ruth comes up with next.</span>
