<span id="freeTextContainer2376016581496781800">DNF at 45%. <br/><br/>How can a mystery/thriller be this slow and this boring? It’s a thriller: give me action. Suspense. And some character development instead. <br/><br/>I happily spoiled myself for the ending. I still didn’t care. I just didn’t care. 😑😑<br/><br/>No wasting time on stories this year that don’t have me invested by the time I’m almost halfway through it. <br/><br/>I’m so annoyed that this was such a flop.</span>

          </span>
