      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/62793178-the-turn-of-the-key">Quotes from The Turn of the Key</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;People do go mad, you know, if you stop them from sleeping for long enough...&rdquo;</span>
